Subject: [MSN] SAFE and the Bayside Historial Society Announce the
	Second	Event in its Spring 2007 Lecture Series: "Preservation
	Imperative"
To: msn-list@te.verweg.com
Message-ID:
	<2C069458-3A5A-4F44-BFF9-B1B88E6E10E9@savingantiquities.org>
